{"tid":1932536,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人聽過超憶症？","createTime":"2020-03-18T19:34:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-19T10:07:01.000Z","uid":15024,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"ed1e3695882bdb3394e41d9c57a274c19a57ca53","tid":1932536,"uid":15024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T19:34:53.000Z","msg":"超憶症，又稱完全記憶，指一個人擁有超常自傳性記憶，可以記住自己一生中主要的個人經歷和事件（無選擇記憶）。<br />\n<br />\n症狀<br />\n這個人不正常地花費大量時間思考自己的過去。<br />\n「病人」具有超常能力回憶自己過去的特定個人事件。<br />\n<br />\n如果你記得哂所有人，同佢地發生嘅事<br />\n但係冇人記得你，或者你對佢印象好深，但實際人地連你係邊個都未必記得<br />\n<br />\n慢慢就會揀左放棄，唔想記得野<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nLIHKG我見冇咩人有討論過依個病，所以好奇想問下"},{"pid":"24ea146d043275452d8175f4fbe2e4d7f3aab7e7","tid":1932536,"uid":8500,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T19:36:01.000Z","msg":"由美國加州大學科學家完成的一項研究指出：全世界患有「超憶症」的只有80人左右。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a810d7bad1410047132d5cf6bed667c9f5ef2e1a","tid":1932536,"uid":337848,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T19:36:33.000Z","msg":"根本係超能力<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db4e32ae05f5749a7d21e1f928b351b82befbb8a","tid":1932536,"uid":24098,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T19:39:00.000Z","msg":"啱啱search過下<br />\n好似係記到每一個細節都背到先算係？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見到啲患者係10年黎每日食咗咩、著咩衫都記得哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8062eea74e0eb646128de2f8a6523b9e6f97c1e0","tid":1932536,"uid":194525,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T19:41:00.000Z","msg":"咁考試咪玩晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1594a1cdcb6e45e33f210fc48b04528a6e99b5f5","tid":1932536,"uid":95761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T19:42:35.000Z","msg":"都唔知應該開心定唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fd18